scripts.deps:update:prod: jq  -r '.dependencies    | keys | .[]' package.json | xargs -n1 -I{} yarn add       {}@latest
scripts.deps:update:dev: jq  -r '.devDependencies | keys | .[]' package.json | xargs -n1 -I{} yarn add --dev {}@latest
scripts.pages: gatsby build && rm -rf docs && mv public/ docs && git add docs && git status
